Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.32,0:00:11.57,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy being a monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.57,0:00:16.91,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm a monster, no matter how many times that golem punched me, I didn't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.32,0:00:22.41,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm a monster, I'm able to stand up to that golem.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:26.83,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I will use my power to protect those I cherish.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.43,0:00:31.80,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm fortunate... to be a monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.80,0:00:32.89,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.89,0:00:34.43,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Like I'll let it end this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.43,0:00:35.26,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Kazaki-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:38.75,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Kazakiri!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.75,0:00:42.33,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Like I'll let it end... in such a stupid way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.51,0:02:37.09,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,If you're looking for Ellis, I had her go ahead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.29,0:02:40.80,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,I should think she's reached her target by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.88,0:02:45.76,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Or perhaps... the target might already have been shredded to chunks of meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.74,0:02:48.14,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You piece of...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.04,0:02:50.53,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,That's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.53,0:02:53.02,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,You just stay here and be my opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:54.74,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately that girl got by.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.74,0:02:55.86,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Kazakiri?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.72,0:02:59.44,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared you were able to destroy Ellis.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.44,0:03:01.28,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,I want war.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.46,0:03:04.62,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.63,0:03:09.04,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,There's still a balance between\Nmagic and science, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:10.28,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:15.65,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,When espers use magic, their body will be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:17.34,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,You've heard of that at least?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:19.05,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.47,0:03:21.72,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you think that was weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:24.17,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,How would anyone know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.28,0:03:29.14,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Because someone tried to, around twenty years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:32.25,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,back when there was a movement to have magic and science walk together,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:34.39,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,which was started by one of our inner factions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:39.37,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,They were trying to give birth to a new type of caster that possessed both esper abilities and magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.77,0:03:42.24,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,The result was...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.83,0:03:46.42,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Ellis was my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.36,0:03:53.08,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Ellis was one of the espers brought in by the faction in Academy City.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.77,0:03:57.34,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to the spells I taught her,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:03:59.05,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Ellis ended up spilling all her blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.97,0:04:04.75,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,To save me from the Knights that came to destroy our facility,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.75,0:04:07.66,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Ellis was beaten to death by their maces.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.01,0:04:11.35,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot co-exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.70,0:04:13.44,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Magicians in the world of magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:15.24,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Scientists in the world of science!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.52,0:04:20.98,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't know the boundaries of our own fields properly, the same mistakes will be repeated over and over again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.16,0:04:24.27,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, this is not making any sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.37,0:04:27.49,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,If this is about protecting each other,\Nwhat the hell is starting a war going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.40,0:04:31.29,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you're not actually going to start one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.52,0:04:38.74,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to accomplish what you want,\Nyou just want a situation where they're about to go to war.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.27,0:04:42.21,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me so highly, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:44.68,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you look at me with pity!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.79,0:04:48.85,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,The clay is my ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:52.72,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,And in this abyss surrounded by clay, I am the ruler!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.88,0:04:56.40,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... she's going to destroy the entire tunnel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.57,0:04:57.85,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Everything, crumble down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.04,0:04:59.31,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Like a puppet of mud!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:00.78,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Shit, what should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.90,0:05:02.32,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Touma, did you know this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.35,0:05:07.47,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,The direction and standing position of the caster in the formula used...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:10.36,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Get it wrong just by a little, and it won't function at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.36,0:05:12.56,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know that golden ratio, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:13.62,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,0:05:15.08,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Devour the foolish ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:17.04,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Melt them into the mud!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.28,0:05:21.00,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,The magic seals on the walls and ceiling are used to bury me alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:23.96,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,And I will recompose your body with all this mud!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:28.39,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Then, she didn't need to have seals on the ground, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:33.31,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,That must mean these seals are the ones that protect her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:34.73,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.25,0:05:39.15,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,It stopped-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.67,0:05:54.74,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.03,0:05:56.95,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.85,0:06:04.25,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,I need to... create war... the reason for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.26,0:06:08.25,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Academy City is letting down its guard too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.67,0:06:15.03,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Even the Church is letting an outsider have possession of Index Librorum Prohibitorum, showing their naivety.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:18.62,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,It was the same situation that occurred during Ellis' time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:21.77,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,A tragedy of that scale took place back then when there were just small factions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.53,0:06:27.13,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,If Academy City and the English Purist Church in their entireties are joining hands-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.13,0:06:28.31,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,This is pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.52,0:06:32.62,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and be angry. Be sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:35.97,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,But, what the hell did Kazakiri do then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.97,0:06:38.21,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What did Index do to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:40.62,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You point your weapon at someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.62,0:06:43.41,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...and that's when real wars happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:45.76,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:47.23,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.23,0:06:50.68,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,I want to slaughter all magicians and espers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.68,0:06:53.21,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.21,0:06:57.61,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't want magicians and espers fighting each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.41,0:07:02.85,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,My mind was in conflict from the very beginning...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:08.08,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,I have more than one conviction...\NI have as many as the number of stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.76,0:07:11.35,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you realize...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.88,0:07:15.90,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...that there was only one thing\Nyou believed in from the very beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.36,0:07:22.08,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, you just didn't want to lose your dear friend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.33,0:07:28.51,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,In your eyes, did Index look like she didn't want to be with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:33.84,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Did we look like we were going to fight unless we were isolated in our own separate worlds?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.48,0:07:38.17,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,We are able to live together without doing such things!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.75,0:07:41.60,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,So don't take my dear friend away from me either!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:44.69,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Intimus115!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:51.57,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.91,0:07:54.53,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,When she said she has as many convictions as the number of stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:57.16,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Die, esper!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:07:58.83,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You understood the one emotion inside you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:03.33,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...of wanting someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.89,0:08:09.84,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...to stop you, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.41,0:08:20.80,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,This may be bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.80,0:08:23.48,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Long distance manipulation has been switched to automaton mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:24.60,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I can't interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.45,0:08:26.55,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Ellis...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.67,0:08:30.56,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,I can't reach you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.56,0:08:33.57,Default,SC,0000,0000,0000,,Ellis...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:38.49,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Kazakiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:39.53,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Index!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.09,0:08:46.16,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:06.39,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouka?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.25,0:09:14.74,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Hyou... ka...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.14,0:09:16.15,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Run.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.90,0:09:18.27,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.27,0:09:20.53,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,It's still dangerous here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:43.83,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,The golem went berserk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.83,0:09:46.39,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,It might be losing control of its regeneration ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.07,0:09:54.23,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouka, let's run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.23,0:09:56.55,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,You hurry and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.55,0:09:57.67,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "you"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.67,0:09:59.48,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Hyouka?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.48,0:10:02.24,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I need to stop that monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.52,0:10:03.52,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.52,0:10:06.89,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,You can't think that you can fight a monster like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.89,0:10:09.90,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, you'll die for sure, Hyouka!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.42,0:10:12.47,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:15.71,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not human either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.67,0:10:19.84,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... for not telling you all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:22.97,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouka!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.86,0:10:46.58,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,The ones to fight monsters... must also be monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.09,0:10:49.62,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go back there anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.62,0:10:52.82,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,That "time" will never happen again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:57.63,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.16,0:11:00.93,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I can't abandon her!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:02.89,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouka!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:07.06,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Because... she's my friend!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.06,0:11:09.57,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Kazakiri!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.91,0:11:13.65,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.07,0:11:16.09,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.66,0:11:20.40,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...that there's still hope in the world you reside in...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:22.95,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...and that I'd show you that!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.93,0:11:35.04,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,It's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.32,0:11:40.51,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,...and so is the nice illusion...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.88,0:12:00.36,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's so messy here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.32,0:12:03.30,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,What is all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:07.46,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me this is your doing, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.91,0:12:10.52,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,You know, while this does happen all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.52,0:12:13.19,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,how much trouble do you have to get yourself into?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.53,0:12:27.41,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.88,0:12:30.59,Default,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,My, Oneesama!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.59,0:12:31.80,Default,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,There you are-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.83,0:12:36.28,Default,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... Oneesama, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.93,0:12:40.11,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.77,0:12:44.93,Default,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,In the very near future,\NJudgment and Anti-Skill will come after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.93,0:12:47.53,Default,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,Before this gets bad, let's run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:49.33,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I said this wasn't-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.30,0:13:15.31,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I knew from the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:18.38,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone knew, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:24.01,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,When a monster reveals its true nature, they know what happens next.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.50,0:13:27.85,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.33,0:13:30.83,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,But what could I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.35,0:13:32.74,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,A friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.10,0:13:36.57,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,A person who called me a friend for the first time in my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.57,0:13:38.31,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to save her...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.76,0:13:46.13,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Why must I lose this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:51.45,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Why must I be afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:54.94,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.67,0:14:01.94,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I just didn't want my dear friend to get hurt!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.48,0:14:04.90,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I stood up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.85,0:14:08.48,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to be with her forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.48,0:14:11.58,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that I could be good friends with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:15.92,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,But... it was impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.61,0:14:19.34,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,...even if she became scared of me... hated me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.34,0:14:22.93,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,...I couldn't watch her get killed!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.57,0:14:28.67,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Do you feel pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.60,0:14:31.66,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Do you feel sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.82,0:14:39.60,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, then you're not a monster, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:48.86,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I know this sounds corny, but you're human.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.41,0:14:50.57,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I guarantee that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:53.10,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.21,0:14:56.47,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Your illusion isn't over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.93,0:15:03.83,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.33,0:15:11.36,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.90,0:15:13.89,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.43,0:15:21.12,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... not human...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:29.63,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,...yet why is she looking at me... as a friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:35.69,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, maybe your composition is a bit different from a human's,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.69,0:15:39.08,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,and you might be able to do things other people can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.68,0:15:41.91,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:51.78,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,But, it doesn't change the fact that you're Index's friend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.88,0:15:57.22,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,You happy now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:16:03.94,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're another step closer to the completion of a key...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:05.61,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,...that can control the Imaginary Number Sector - Five Elements Institution.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.52,0:16:09.48,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, you're a monster to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.15,0:16:15.32,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,To think that the Imaginary Number Sector's true nature is the AIM dispersion field itself...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:17.08,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure no one would think of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:22.14,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Then, to be adding self-consciousness to and helping the materialization of something like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:23.97,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you to be sane at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:26.99,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking, Aleister?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:29.22,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.76,0:16:35.57,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,The Imaginary Number Sector is a kind of aggregation of power that exists in a separate dimension from humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.02,0:16:38.69,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,An organism born from that aggregation is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.20,0:16:42.99,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,I know what that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:45.49,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,An angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.58,0:16:51.48,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,If the inhabitants of the Imaginary Number Sector,\Nlike Kazakiri, were "Angels" per se,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.88,0:16:55.35,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,then the city in which they live in would be... in other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.63,0:17:00.45,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're trying to artificially create Heaven?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:05.67,Default,Crowley,0000,0000,0000,,Throwing words like "Angels" and "Heaven" at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.20,0:17:07.38,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Cut me some slack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:09.50,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,As if there'd be someone who'd know more than you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.32,0:17:13.46,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Aleister Crowley, the magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.86,0:17:19.78,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,From this time's incident,\Nthe world has slowly begun to tremble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.23,0:17:25.17,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,You purposely lured in a member of the English Purist Church and defeated her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.89,0:17:31.67,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,What you're thinking is completely beyond me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.67,0:17:36.20,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,But if you're going to take advantage of that Imagine Breaker, then be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.42,0:17:42.74,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,Face him with half-assed beliefs,\Nand his right hand will eat your illusions alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.07,0:17:51.47,Default,Crowley,0000,0000,0000,,The illusions I believed in... are already in a destroyed state since long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.91,0:17:56.82,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.82,0:17:59.41,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I'm completely unscratched!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.41,0:18:01.26,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, I'm good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:03.52,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,This is a sign that I'm learning, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.52,0:18:04.47,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.47,0:18:06.81,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Kamijyo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.81,0:18:13.36,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,You really, really, really LOVE causing trouble for others, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.71,0:18:17.61,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, for you to be in Anti-Skill's custody...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.44,0:18:23.52,Default,Aisa,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I told you to be careful of Kazakiri Hyouka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.41,0:18:31.49,Default,Aisa,0000,0000,0000,,Your personality of going all out when it comes to women needs a good amount of tweaking sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.49,0:18:36.58,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, these two people in the back scare me,\Nso could I stay in the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.58,0:18:39.13,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,In absolute-rest, no-visitor conditions-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.75,0:18:43.38,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,U-Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.38,0:18:44.72,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Your skirt...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:47.06,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to fix it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.84,0:18:49.59,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Is it that weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.05,0:18:52.13,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.55,0:18:54.42,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I really think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.12,0:18:57.24,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,It was already weird to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:18:59.63,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,It might be even weirder now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.63,0:19:01.03,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.35,0:19:07.08,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouka, you-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.36,0:19:09.13,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:13.79,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,My body is like a lump of esper power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.28,0:19:20.89,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what I do, it'll never change the fact that I'm an unstable entity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.89,0:19:23.75,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Is this because of Touma's right hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.75,0:19:24.75,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.46,0:19:31.43,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,If his powers really affected me,\Nthen I would've been gone already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:34.96,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.96,0:19:40.89,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,About his power, I don't know too much about it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.81,0:19:44.94,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Esper abilities, alone, aren't enough to explain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.27,0:19:49.42,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Now then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:51.60,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouka?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.70,0:19:57.67,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I need to go back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.33,0:20:01.51,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouka!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:11.54,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you worry, I'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.54,0:20:15.64,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,My body is formed from the powers of many, many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.16,0:20:21.34,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I did disappear, it wouldn't mean I'd died.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.34,0:20:24.10,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,It'd just mean you wouldn't be able to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.90,0:20:27.50,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you can't tell,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:31.00,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,I will always be by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.95,0:20:34.90,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouka...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.79,0:20:41.55,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,We'll hang out together again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.46,0:20:43.53,Default,Hyouka,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.99,0:20:56.56,Default,Maika,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}Like I said, second semester is very busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.56,0:20:59.44,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}But I have so much time, I'm bored!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.44,0:21:02.90,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}Touma wouldn't pay attention to me or play with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.48,0:21:08.11,Default,blue,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}Look, this is what magicians should look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.11,0:21:09.49,Default,blue,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}Moe, right? Moe, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:12.27,Default,blue,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}Come on, Hime-yan, you do it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.27,0:21:14.16,Default,Aisa,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}Is this... moe then?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.16,0:21:18.33,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}Okay, boys and girls, we're going start homeroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.67,0:21:21.30,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.51,0:21:23.13,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}Where's Tsuchimikado-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.80,0:21:29.60,Default,Tsuchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}Yeah, I started my job already.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.76,0:21:42.87,Default,Yomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}Take care of those two, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.87,0:21:44.56,Default,Yoshi,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:57.62,Default,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.79,0:21:59.04,Default,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}My ribbon has drifted into...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.04,0:22:01.96,Default,Kuroko,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}...Oneesama's forbidden sanctuary!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.96,0:22:03.39,Default,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}KUROKO!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.24,0:22:23.44,Default,Laura,0000,0000,0000,,A situation has arisen where we need\Nthe Index Librorum Prohibitorum's assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.47,0:22:26.85,Default,Laura,0000,0000,0000,,Have her keeper come, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.85,0:22:28.82,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,"Keeper", eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.31,0:22:30.56,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.56,0:22:32.49,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Kanzaki and I will leave for Japan right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.42,0:22:36.45,Default,Laura,0000,0000,0000,,The problem, however, is we cannot contact Kanzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.27,0:22:39.95,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, Archbishop?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.27,0:22:43.75,Default,Laura,0000,0000,0000,,I am wearing a rather dull attire for a change,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.75,0:22:46.13,Default,Laura,0000,0000,0000,,you shan't address me by my formal title.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.50,0:22:48.93,Default,Laura,0000,0000,0000,,Laura Stuart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.36,0:22:51.21,Default,Laura,0000,0000,0000,,You shall address me by that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.64,0:22:56.60,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Sign: Daihasei Festival - the strongest in Academy City
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.45,0:23:04.77,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, Index-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.90,0:23:10.53,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma, you forgot the fridge was empty, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.49,0:23:15.51,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma, eating something delicious all by yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.36,0:23:18.91,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, this is leftover from lunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.08,0:23:22.14,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma, you're the only one who even had a lunch, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.19,0:23:27.84,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry, I'm hungry, I'm hungry!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.90,0:23:33.15,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Such misfortune!!!
